<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_4905a6bc-77eb-431a-93b3-ba04b55845d3" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>8.4.5</sptc><title id="_5c150ad5-ad47-414b-a228-18986798fd83">Glazed panels, other than doors or side panels, on the perimeter of rooms</title><archive-num>2019: 3.6.4.4</archive-num><subclause id="_ada20aff-b15a-49be-a653-0293777db3d6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_5aeecfef-313f-4a9f-8cd9-20cd8a251627">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>All framed glazing where the lowest sight line of the glazing panel is less than 500 mm from the highest abutting finished floor level (see <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/719_0.19.0.xml#_e2a8e26d-1db4-4c2d-9952-57e435d4051b" id="_bf054fee-ae16-4c75-be5f-0c1ca2ef88cc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 8.4.5</xref>) must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_87c90069-1102-4c8a-8349-a3b40e549b1b">Grade A safety glazing material in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/429_0.8.0.xml#_683329b1-c0f9-41f3-a7ec-31daa9e94819" id="_e68abaa5-b0b9-4160-ab68-1faf4644f5ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table 8.4.2</xref>; or</li><li id="_07ac0273-e264-4a21-842b-8cacba8b2313">monolithic annealed glass not less than 5 mm nominal thickness provided that the area of the glazing panel is not more than 1.2 m<sup id="_0fa30dbd-f05d-4dc1-84bd-e98da8a2cc0b">2</sup>.</li></ol></subclause><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/719_0.19.0.xml" id="_e2a8e26d-1db4-4c2d-9952-57e435d4051b"><num xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" inv:access="external">8.4.5</num><title xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_b1a3f060-b77d-4956-aca2-afe5f33fdbcc" inv:access="external">Identification of glazing requirements for glazed panels</title><image xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:8-3-5-identification-of-glazing-requirements-for-glazed-panels.eps" inv:access="external"/></image-reference></clause>